		<header class="entry-header"><h1 class="entry-title">COVID-19 Update</h1>					<ul class="entry-meta">
<li class="author">
					<span>Posted by</span>
					<a href="http://www.paradiseesd.org/author/admin/">staff</a>				</li>
								<li class="entry-category">
					<span>Categories</span> <a href="http://www.paradiseesd.org/category/news/" rel="category tag">News</a>				</li>
								<li class="entry-date">
